<div style='direction:ltr;border-width:100%'>

<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:8.684in'>

<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:8.684in'>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>二级缓存是全局缓存，是一个基于</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>namespace</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>级别的缓存，作用域更为广泛，不局限于一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>sqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，可以在多个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>sqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>之间共享，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>mybatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的二级缓存默认也是开启的，但是由于它的作用域是</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>namespace</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，所以还需要在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>mapper.xml</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>中开启才能生效，只需要加入</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>cache</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>标签即可。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>二级缓存的数据存放在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSessionFactory</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSessionFactory</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>实例是线程安全的，只要是同一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSessionFactory</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>对象创建的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，在进行查询时都能共享数据。一般在项目中只有一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSessionFactory</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>对象，所以二级缓存的数据是全项目共享的。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>实际上</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MyBatis </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>新增了一个装饰器的类（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>CachingExecutor</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）来维护二级缓存。如果启用了二级缓存，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>CachingExecutor
     </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>对于查询请求，会判断二级缓存是否有缓存结果，如果有，就直接返回，如果没有，就交给本地缓存</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> / </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>一级缓存
     （</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>local cache</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）的查询器</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Executor </span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>实现类</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=418 height=204></p>

<p style='margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>当要访问数据库形成一个会话查询一条数据时，这个数据就会被放在当前会话的一级缓存中，如果这个时候会话关闭了，那么以及缓存中的数据会被保存到二级缓存中，新的会话查询信息就会参照二级缓存。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>也就是说只有一级缓存被关闭或者提交以后，一级缓存数据才会转移到二级缓存</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt;color:black'><span style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>二级缓存是事务性的。</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MyBatis </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>为了保证数据的一致性和可靠性，只有在事务完成时才会将数据更新到缓存中，这样可以避免在事务未完成时读取到脏数据。当</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SqlSession </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>完成并提交时，或是完成并回滚，但没有执行</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> flushCache=true </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> insert/delete/update
     </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>语句时，缓存会获得更新。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>二级缓存支持多种</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Cache</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的方式，并且可以接入外部分布式缓存中间件，缓存的功能更为丰富</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>二级缓存极易出现脏数据，如果是分布式环境，使用本地存储，必然会造成脏数据，所以一定要使用分布式缓存中间件避免</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>二级缓存在多表操作时，或者</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>namespace</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>设置不合理时，基于出现脏数据，而且排查起来困难，多表查询可能跨越多个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>namespace</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，如果没有指定</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>cache-ref</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的话，极易读取到脏数据</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:13.5pt;color:black'><span style='font-weight:bold'>开启二级缓存</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>开启二级缓存，只需要 在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Mapper.xml </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>文件中配置</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> &lt;cache/&gt; </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>标签</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>二级缓存启用后，会有以下效果：</span></li>
 <ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
  0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
  font-style:normal'>
  <li value=1 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:
      normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>映射语句文件中的所有</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
      font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> select </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:
      normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>语句的结果将会被缓存。</span></li>
 </ol>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
 0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
 font-style:normal'>
 <li value=2 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>映射语句文件中的所有</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> insert</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>、</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>update </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>和</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> delete </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>语句会刷新缓存。</span></li>
</ol>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
 0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
 font-style:normal'>
 <li value=3 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>缓存会使用最近最少使用算法（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>LRU, Least
     Recently Used</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>）算法来清除不需要的缓存。</span></li>
</ol>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
 0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
 font-style:normal'>
 <li value=4 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>缓存不会定时进行刷新（也就是说，没有刷新间隔）。</span></li>
</ol>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
 0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
 font-style:normal'>
 <li value=5 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>缓存会保存列表或对象（无论查询方法返回哪种）的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> 1024 </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>个引用。</span></li>
</ol>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
 0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
 font-style:normal'>
 <li value=6 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>缓存会被视为读</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>/</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
     font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>写缓存，这意味着获取到的对象并不是共享的，可以安全地被调用者修改，而不干扰其他调用者或线程所做的潜在修改。</span></li>
</ol>

  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;

  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>eviction</p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  vertical-align:top;width:7.3in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt;
  color:black'>二级缓存的清除策略</p>
  <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
       style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>LRU</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
  font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>最近最少使用：移除最长时间不被使用的对象。</p>
  <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
       style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>FIFO</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
  font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>先进先出：按对象进入缓存的顺序来移除它们。</p>
  <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
       style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>SOFT</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
  font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>软引用：基于垃圾回收器状态和软引用规则移除对象。</p>
  <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
       style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>WEAK</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
  font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>弱引用：更积极地基于垃圾收集器状态和弱引用规则移除对象</p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:.9395in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>flushInterval</p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:7.35in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
  color:black' lang=zh-CN>缓存的刷新间隔，</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
  color:black' lang=en-US>1000=1s</span></p>
  <p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt'>可以被设置为任意的正整数，设置的值应该是一个以毫秒为单位的合理时间量。
  默认情况是不设置，也就是没有刷新间隔，缓存仅仅会在调用语句时刷新</p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:white;vertical-align:top;width:.9201in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'
  lang=en-US>size</p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:white;vertical-align:top;width:7.3in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>引用数目，默认值是</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> 1024</span></p>
  <p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt'>性可以被设置为任意正整数，要注意欲缓存对象的大小和运行环境中可用的内存资源。</p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:.9201in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>readOnly</p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:7.3694in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
  color:black'>返回的对象是否只读，</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>true </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>或</span><span style='font-family:
  "Comic Sans MS"'> false</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>（默认）</span></p>
  <p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt'>只读的缓存会给所有调用者返回缓存对象的相同实例。
  因此这些对象不能被修改。这就提供了可观的性能提升。而可读写的缓存会（通过序列化）返回缓存对象的拷贝。 速度上会慢一些，但是更安全</p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

</div>

<p style='margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#000088'>&lt;cache</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#000088'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span><span
style='color:#660066'>eviction</span><span style='color:#666600'>=</span><span
style='color:#008800'>&quot;FIFO&quot;</span><span style='color:#000088'><br>
<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span><span style='color:#660066'>flushInterval</span><span
style='color:#666600'>=</span><span style='color:#008800'>&quot;60000&quot;</span><span
style='color:#000088'><br>
<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span><span style='color:#660066'>size</span><span
style='color:#666600'>=</span><span style='color:#008800'>&quot;512&quot;</span><span
style='color:#000088'><br>
<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span><span style='color:#660066'>readOnly</span><span
style='color:#666600'>=</span><span style='color:#008800'>&quot;true&quot;</span><span
style='color:#000088'>/&gt;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#000088'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:7pt;
     margin-bottom:7pt;color:black'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>这个更高级的配置创建了一个</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'> FIFO </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>缓存，每隔</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'> 60 </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>秒刷新，最多可以存储结果对象或列表的</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'> 512 </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>个引用，而且返回的对象被认为是只读的，因此对它们进行修改可能会在不同线程中的调用者产生冲突</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt;color:#333333'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:7pt;
     margin-bottom:7pt'><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
     12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MyBatis</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>一级缓存存放的是对象，二级缓存存放的是对象的数据。所以要求二级缓存存放的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>实体类</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>必须是可序列化的，也就是要实现</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Serializable</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>接口。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'><span style='color:#C00000' lang=zh-CN>public class</span><span
lang=zh-CN> Student </span><span style='color:#C00000' lang=zh-CN>implements</span><span
lang=zh-CN> Serializable {</span><span lang=en-US> … }</span></p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>实现</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Serializable</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>接口并不是必须的，如果不需要使用二级缓存，那么实体类可以不实现</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Serializable</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>接口。但是如果使用了二级缓存，而实体类没有实现</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Serializable</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>接口，则会抛出</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>NotSerializableException</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>异常。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-size:13.5pt'><span style='font-weight:bold;
font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>引用其他缓存</span><span style='font-weight:bold;
font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#333333'>cache-ref</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-size:12.0pt;
color:#333333'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>对某一命名空间的语句，只会使用该命名空间的缓存进行缓存或刷新。
但你可能会想要在多个命名空间中共享相同的缓存配置和实例。要实现这种需求，你可以使用</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>
cache-ref </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>元素来引用另一个缓存。</span></p>

<p style='margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#000088'>&lt;cache-ref </span><span
style='color:#660066'>namespace</span><span style='color:#666600'>=</span><span
style='color:#008800'>&quot;com.someone.application.data.SomeMapper&quot;</span><span
style='color:#000088'>/&gt;</span></p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:13.5pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>清空二级缓存（生命周期）</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>如果进行了数据更新操作，那么这个操作会立即清空缓存，下次查询时会重新从数据库中获取数据。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:0pt;
     margin-bottom:7pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>但如果你想在特定的</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> SQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>语句改变默认的行为，只需要使用设置其</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>
     flushCache </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>即可，</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>flushCache</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>=true </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>时会同时清除一级缓存和二级缓存。比如，某些情况下你可能希望特定一条</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> select </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>语句清空缓存。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#000088' lang=zh-CN>&lt;select</span><span
style='color:black' lang=zh-CN> ... </span><span style='color:#660066'
lang=zh-CN>flushCache</span><span style='color:#666600' lang=zh-CN>=</span><span
style='color:#008800' lang=zh-CN>&quot;</span><span style='color:#008800'
lang=en-US>true</span><span style='color:#008800' lang=zh-CN>&quot;</span><span
style='color:#000088' lang=zh-CN>/&gt;</span><span style='color:black'
lang=zh-CN><br>
</span><span style='color:#000088' lang=zh-CN>&lt;insert</span><span
style='color:black' lang=zh-CN> ... </span><span style='color:#660066'
lang=zh-CN>flushCache</span><span style='color:#666600' lang=zh-CN>=</span><span
style='color:#008800' lang=zh-CN>&quot;true&quot;</span><span style='color:
#000088' lang=zh-CN>/&gt;</span><span style='color:black' lang=zh-CN><br>
</span><span style='color:#000088' lang=zh-CN>&lt;update</span><span
style='color:black' lang=zh-CN> ... </span><span style='color:#660066'
lang=zh-CN>flushCache</span><span style='color:#666600' lang=zh-CN>=</span><span
style='color:#008800' lang=zh-CN>&quot;true&quot;</span><span style='color:
#000088' lang=zh-CN>/&gt;</span><span style='color:black' lang=zh-CN><br>
</span><span style='color:#000088' lang=zh-CN>&lt;delete</span><span
style='color:black' lang=zh-CN> ... </span><span style='color:#660066'
lang=zh-CN>flushCache</span><span style='color:#666600' lang=zh-CN>=</span><span
style='color:#008800' lang=zh-CN>&quot;true&quot;</span><span style='color:
#000088' lang=zh-CN>/&gt;</span></p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:13.5pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>禁用二级缓存</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> MyBatis </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>中，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&lt;setting&gt; </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>元素用于配置框架的各种设置。其中，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>cacheEnabled </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>参数是二级缓存全局开关。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#24292F'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&lt;settings&gt;</p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&lt;setting name=&quot;<span style='color:#F73131'>cacheEnabled</span>&quot;
value=&quot;<span style='color:#F73131'>true</span>&quot;/&gt; </p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&lt;/settings&gt;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>cacheEnabled</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;设置的默认值是&nbsp;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>true</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，也就是默认情况下&nbsp;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;会启用二级缓存功能。如果不需要缓存功能，可以将该设置显式地设置为&nbsp;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>false</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;来禁用全局的二级缓存。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:0pt;
     margin-bottom:7pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>但如果你想在特定的</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> SQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>语句改变默认的行为，只需要使用设置其</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> useCache </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>即可，默认情况下查询会被二级缓存，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>u</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>seCache</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>=false </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>时会禁用二级缓存。比如，某些情况下你可能希望特定一条</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> select </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>语句清空缓存。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#000088' lang=zh-CN>&lt;select</span><span
style='color:black' lang=zh-CN> ... </span><span style='color:#660066'
lang=zh-CN>useCache</span><span style='color:#666600' lang=zh-CN>=</span><span
style='color:#008800' lang=zh-CN>&quot;</span><span style='color:#008800'
lang=en-US>false</span><span style='color:#008800' lang=zh-CN>&quot;</span><span
style='color:#000088' lang=zh-CN>/&gt;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#000088'>&nbsp;</p>
